<plot>It began with a phone call... LAPD's Detective Daniel spends happy days with his wife, Laura, and his daughter, Mandy. Daniel goes to the place where murder case happened with his junior partner, Jack. At the murder place, Jack, turns into strange. On their way to home, Jack asks Daniel "Do you believe in Death?" and Daniel just laughs at that moment. Right after that, Daniel meets a guy who has a phone which dial the past only two times. Next day, Daniel founds Jack dead when he visits him, and Daniel notices the guy in yesterday was real Death. He starts the battle for his dearest wife and child with DEATH PHONE which can dial the past.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?133867</url></doc>
